column5: Hey everyone I'm looking to spend around $400 can anyone recomend a good fish finder for around that price?

Eagle FISHELITE 642C IGPS 5-Inch bought from Radio world last month, only used it once last week and loved it I paid $385.00 and $130.. for the hotmaps chip  I asked the same question a while ago and 3 people came back with this suggestion Also it only took me 1 hour to install and get working
Thanks Ill look into that I know where Radio World is Ive just never been in there..
Use this link and check out your options before you go.  http://radioworld.ca/index.php
